📆 QOTD Protocol 📆

1️⃣ The format/template you are to use is as follows:

@everyone Daily Question :bookmark:

 **-** [Question]
2️⃣ Avoid questions that can be answered with a yes/no, questions should be open ended & encourage debate.

3️⃣ Topics should not be too specific, i.e avoid questions such as “Which of Empeor Justinian’s 2nd reign military generals were the best at strategic warfare”
